'''極光大麻'''（{{lang-en|Aurora Cannabis}}）是一家總部位於加拿大的[[大麻|大麻]]生產、分銷和銷售商<ref name="SA">{{cite web |title=Canaccord Genuity Remains a Hold on Aurora Cannabis (ACB) |url=https://www.smarteranalyst.com/new-blurbs/canaccord-genuity-remains-a-hold-on-aurora-cannabis-acb/ |website=Smarter Analyst |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2020-10-07 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112101358/https://www.smarteranalyst.com/new-blurbs/canaccord-genuity-remains-a-hold-on-aurora-cannabis-acb/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於[[紐約證券交易所|紐約證券交易所]]、[[多倫多證券交易所|多倫多證券交易所]]和[[法蘭克福證券交易所|法蘭克福證券交易所]]<ref>{{cite web |title=華泰瑞銀(08006-HK)斥資512.5萬港元投資北美大麻產品業務 |url=https://www.finet.hk/newscenter/news_content/5ff6a5ecbde0b30d4618e60e |website=財華社 |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2021-01-07 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112025332/https://www.finet.hk/newscenter/news_content/5ff6a5ecbde0b30d4618e60e |dead-url=no }}</ref>上市。

== 歷史 ==
[[File:AuroraSky.jpg|缩略图]]的极光大麻温室和总部]]
極光大麻由特里·布思（Terry Booth）和史蒂夫·多布勒（Steve Dobler）於2006年11月21日創辦，總部位於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[愛民頓|愛民頓]]<ref name="SA"/><ref name="CNBC-190313">{{cite web |author1=Thomas Franck |title=Aurora Cannabis pops nearly 14% after billionaire activist investor Nelson Peltz joins as an advisor |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2019/03/13/aurora-cannabis-shares-surge-after-hiring-billionaire-activist-investor-nelson-peltz-as-an-advisor.html |publisher=CNBC |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2019-03-13 |archive-date=2021-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228225126/https://www.cnbc.com/2019/03/13/aurora-cannabis-shares-surge-after-hiring-billionaire-activist-investor-nelson-peltz-as-an-advisor.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。極光大麻於2017年7月24日在[[多倫多證券交易所|多倫多證券交易所]]上市<ref name="cision">{{cite web |title=Aurora Cannabis Starts Trading on Toronto Stock Exchange |url=https://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/aurora-cannabis-starts-trading-on-toronto-stock-exchange-635823983.html |publisher=Cision |access-date=30 November 2019 |date=21 July 2017 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112061248/https://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/aurora-cannabis-starts-trading-on-toronto-stock-exchange-635823983.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於2018年10月23日在[[紐約證券交易所|紐約證券交易所]]上市<ref name="street">{{cite web |author1=Tony Owusu |title=Pot Company Aurora Cannabis Sinks in Its NYSE Debut |url=https://www.thestreet.com/investing/aurora-cannabis-canada-latest-pot-company-debuts-on-nyse-tuesday-14754095 |publisher=The Street |access-date=30 November 2019 |date=23 October 2018 |archive-date=2021-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201011627/https://www.thestreet.com/investing/aurora-cannabis-canada-latest-pot-company-debuts-on-nyse-tuesday-14754095 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，股票代號為'''ACB'''<ref>{{cite web |title=Aurora Cannabis breach exposes personal data of former, current workers |url=https://mjbizdaily.com/aurora-cannabis-breach-exposes-personal-data-of-former-current-employees/ |website=Marijuana Business Daily |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2021-01-04 |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127234441/https://mjbizdaily.com/aurora-cannabis-breach-exposes-personal-data-of-former-current-employees/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年11月13日，極光大麻以每股24加拿大元的價格向{{link-en|CanniMed|CanniMed}}提出全股權收購，並聲稱已獲得後者38%的股東支持<ref name="CBC-171115">{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/business/cannimed-therapeutics-aurora-cannnabis-takeover-bid-1.4403189|title=CanniMed tells shareholders to wait while it reviews Aurora offer|work=CBC News|access-date=2021-01-18|date=2017-11-15|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813181037/https://www.cbc.ca/news/business/cannimed-therapeutics-aurora-cannnabis-takeover-bid-1.4403189|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{link-en|CanniMed|CanniMed}}的行政總裁拒絕有關方案，並表示極光大麻的收購是基於過高的股價。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/business/aurora-cannabis-cannimed-therapeutics-takeover-bid-1.4417757|title=Aurora takeover bid 'makes no sense,' based on inflated share price: CanniMed|work=CBC News|access-date=2021-01-18|date=2017-11-24|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109024857/https://www.cbc.ca/news/business/aurora-cannabis-cannimed-therapeutics-takeover-bid-1.4417757|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年1月初，{{link-en|CanniMed|CanniMed}}更一度入稟控告極光大麻侵害其經濟利益。<ref name="CBC-180124">{{cite web |title=Aurora Cannabis buys CanniMed in Canada's biggest deal |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/business/aurora-cannabis-cannimed-marijuana-1.4501367 |website=CBC |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2018-01-24 |archive-date=2019-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190226111956/https://www.cbc.ca/news/business/aurora-cannabis-cannimed-marijuana-1.4501367 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2018年1月24日，極光大麻宣佈以每股43加拿大元，共11億加拿大元的代價成功收購其競爭對手{{link-en|CanniMed|CanniMed}}，收購完成後極光大麻成為加拿大最高市值的大麻生產商。<ref name="CBC-180124"/>2018年9月，{{link-en|彭博商業新聞台|BNN Bloomberg}}報導[[可口可樂|可口可樂]]正考慮與極光大麻合作開發含有[[大麻二酚|大麻二酚]]的飲料。<ref>{{cite web |title=从咖啡饮品到“大麻饮料” 可口可乐的焦虑与图谋 |url=http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/usstock/c/2018-09-24/doc-ifxeuwwr7567452.shtml |website=新浪財經 |publisher=國際金融報 |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2018-09-24 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112044735/http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/usstock/c/2018-09-24/doc-ifxeuwwr7567452.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>可口可樂與極光大麻其後澄清有關計劃仍處於討論階段，尚未簽署任何協議。<ref>{{cite web|author=Christina Pellegrini|title=Aurora says there isn't a deal with Coca-Cola on marijuana-based drinks|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/cannabis/article-aurora-responds-to-report-of-talks-with-coca-cola/|website=Globe and Mail|access-date=18 September 2018|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108105624/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/cannabis/article-aurora-responds-to-report-of-talks-with-coca-cola/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年，極光大麻宣佈以接近2000萬加拿大元的認股權為代價，邀得美國富翁{{link-en|納爾遜·佩茲|Nelson Peltz}}擔任策略顧問<ref name="CBC-190313">{{cite web |title=Aurora Cannabis shares jump after U.S. billionaire Peltz named as advisor |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/business/aurora-cannabis-nelson-peltz-1.5054445 |website=CBC |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2019-03-13 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107230856/https://www.cbc.ca/news/business/aurora-cannabis-nelson-peltz-1.5054445 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，極光大麻的股價其後下跌約96%，納爾遜·佩茲亦於2020年辭任策略顧問一職。他任職其間極光大麻錄得至少35億加拿大元的虧損。<ref name="CBC-200928">{{cite web |title=Aurora Cannabis, billionaire Nelson Peltz ‘have concluded their relationship’ |url=https://mjbizdaily.com/aurora-cannabis-nelson-peltz-have-concluded-their-relationship/ |website=CBC |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2020-09-28 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124203537/https://mjbizdaily.com/aurora-cannabis-nelson-peltz-have-concluded-their-relationship// |dead-url=no }}</ref>

極光大麻於2020財政年度錄得33億加拿大元的虧損。2020年6月，極光大麻宣佈辭退約700名員工，並關閉位於[[薩斯喀徹溫|薩斯喀徹溫]]、[[安大略省|安大略省]]、[[亞伯達省|亞伯達省]]和[[魁北克市|魁北克市]]的生產設施。<ref name="CBC-210110">{{cite web |title=Aurora Cannabis lays off 30 staff, 'indefinitely' pauses operations at Alta. facility |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/aurora-cannabis-pausing-operations-layoffs-1.5823178 |website=CBC |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2020-12-01 |archive-date=2020-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220132835/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/aurora-cannabis-pausing-operations-layoffs-1.5823178 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="CBC-200624">{{cite web |title=Aurora Cannabis to lay off staff, close 5 sites in 4 provinces |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/aurora-cannabis-to-lay-off-staff-close-5-sites-in-4-provinces-1.5623780 |website=CBC |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2020-06-24 |archive-date=2020-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220132944/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/aurora-cannabis-to-lay-off-staff-close-5-sites-in-4-provinces-1.5623780 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2020年2月，創辦人布思宣佈退休並由麥可·辛格（Michael Singer）接任行政總裁。<ref>{{cite web |title=Aurora Cannabis to take C$1 billion in charges, cuts 500 jobs as CEO exits |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-aurora-cannabis-ceo/aurora-cannabis-to-take-c1-billion-in-charges-cuts-500-jobs-as-ceo-exits-idUSKBN2002TY |publisher=Reuters |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2020-02-07 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112203146/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-aurora-cannabis-ceo/aurora-cannabis-to-take-c1-billion-in-charges-cuts-500-jobs-as-ceo-exits-idUSKBN2002TY |dead-url=no }}</ref>2020年5月28日，極光大麻以價值4000萬美元的股份完成收購美國大麻二酚產品銷售商{{link-en|Reliva|Reliva}}<ref name="PR-200528">{{cite web |title=Aurora Cannabis Completes Acquisition of Reliva LLC |url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/aurora-cannabis-completes-acquisition-of-reliva-llc-301067122.html |website=[[PR_Newswire|PR Newswire]] |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2020-05-28 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112101248/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/aurora-cannabis-completes-acquisition-of-reliva-llc-301067122.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Aurora Cannabis to Buy CBD Retailer Reliva for $40 Million in Stock |url=https://www.newcannabisventures.com/aurora-cannabis-to-buy-cbd-retailer-reliva-for-40-million-in-stock/ |website=New Cannabis Ventures |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2020-05-20 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126120335/https://www.newcannabisventures.com/aurora-cannabis-to-buy-cbd-retailer-reliva-for-40-million-in-stock/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{link-en|Reliva|Reliva}}的行政總裁米格爾·馬丁（Miguel Martin）於同年9月8日取代辛格接任極光大麻行政總裁。<ref name="MotleyFool-210105">{{cite web |title=Why Can't Aurora Cannabis Land a Deal? |url=https://www.fool.com/investing/2021/01/05/why-cant-aurora-cannabis-land-a-deal/ |website=The Motley Fool |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2021-01-05 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128054313/https://www.fool.com/investing/2021/01/05/why-cant-aurora-cannabis-land-a-deal/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Aurora Cannabis names new CEO, expects up to $1.8B in goodwill impairment charges |url=https://globalnews.ca/news/7322624/aurora-cannabis-ceo-martin-reliva/ |website=Global News |publisher=The Canadian Press |accessdate=2021-01-10 |date=2020-09-08 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112041040/https://globalnews.ca/news/7322624/aurora-cannabis-ceo-martin-reliva/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年12月25日，極光大麻遭到駭客入侵。據科技新聞網站{{link-en|Bleeping Computer|Bleeping Computer}}報導，約50GB的資料被駭客盜取。駭客在網上公開了被盜資料的樣本，其中包括員工護照和駕駛執照、支票和其他商業資料的資料，並要求極光大麻支付一枚[[比特幣|比特幣]]以換取資料不被公開。<ref>{{cite web |author1=Jeff Lagerquist |title=Hacked Aurora Cannabis data for sale after Christmas Day attack |url=https://ca.finance.yahoo.com/news/hacked-aurora-cannabis-data-for-sale-after-christmas-day-attack-202058896.html |website=Yahoo Finance Canada |accessdate=2021-01-19 |date=2021-01-12 |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120124658/https://ca.finance.yahoo.com/news/hacked-aurora-cannabis-data-for-sale-after-christmas-day-attack-202058896.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Lawrence Abrams |title=Hacker sells Aurora Cannabis files stolen in Christmas cyberattack |url=https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/hacker-sells-aurora-cannabis-files-stolen-in-christmas-cyberattack/ |publisher={{link-en|Bleeping Computer|Bleeping Computer}} |accessdate=2021-01-19 |date=2021-01-07 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123022241/https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/hacker-sells-aurora-cannabis-files-stolen-in-christmas-cyberattack/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

